---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Join Us">
  <PageHero
    eyebrow="Join the choir"
    title="No audition. Just come and sing."
    text="VOX Holloway welcomes new singers with or without choir experience. You do not need to read music, and you do not need to know your voice part before you arrive."
    image="/images/community-choir.jpg"
    ctaLabel="Email us about joining"
    ctaHref="mailto:hello@voxholloway.com?subject=Joining VOX Holloway"
  />
  <section class="section section-tight">
    <div class="grid cards">
      <article class="info-card">
        <h3>1. Say hello</h3>
        <p>Send us a quick message and we will tell you when the next open rehearsal is happening.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="info-card">
        <h3>2. Try a rehearsal</h3>
        <p>Come along, listen, join in, and meet the choir. There is no pressure to know everything straight away.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="info-card">
        <h3>3. Stay for the term</h3>
        <p>If it feels right, we will help you settle into the current project and get access to rehearsal materials.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="prose">
    <h1>What to expect</h1>
    <p>Rehearsals are friendly, focused, and full of people learning together. Bring water, a pencil, and a willingness to make sound before everything is perfect.</p>
    <p>VOX is especially suited to singers who want community, consistency, and the joy of working towards performances with real musical ambition.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
